cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.IR 

The paper deals with natural language processing and network science to identify the political ideology of news articles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses advances in representation learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of network science suggests the possibility of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval, which falls under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
